    "The document stride determines the starting token of each subsequent chunk.",
    "After this preprocessing step, each chunk prepended with the original question tokens is considered a separate data sample.",
    "We use clinical notes sourced from the VA Corporate Data Warehouse (CDW) to construct the gold-standard dataset.",
    "The clinical notes in the VA CDW are fully identified.",
    "The selected notes correspond to the period of January 2022 and belong to patients with the Hepatitis C diagnosis."
